// @test syntax/comments
// @description Comment syntax. Single-line // comments are the only comment form Pine has - /* */ block comments are NOT valid (TV lexes `/` `*` as operators and errors CE10156; probed - see INV043). The block comments below are consumed as trivia for recovery but each line-leading one reports TV's 'Syntax error at input "new line"' at column 1.
// @expects parse: fail
// @expects error: line=7, column=1, message=/Syntax error at input .new line./
// @expects error: line=10, column=1, message=/Syntax error at input .new line./
// @expects error: line=16, column=1, message=/Syntax error at input .new line./

//@version=6
indicator("Comment Tests")

// Single line comment
x = 1 // Trailing comment

/* Block comment on single line */
y = 2

/*
Multi-line
block comment
*/
z = 3

/* Block comment with * asterisks * inside */
w = 4

// Comment with special chars: @#$%^&*(){}[]|
a = 5

plot(x + y + z + w + a)
